\sum|g_n|
k\gt 0
|f_n(x)|\leq k
n\in \mathbb N
x\in X
\sum  |f_ng_n|
\left|\sum_{i=n}^mf_i(x)g_i(x)\right|\le\sum_{i=n}^m|f_i(x)||g_i(x)|\stackrel{\forall\,x\in X}\le k\sum_{i=n}^n|g_i(x)|
n,m>N_\epsilon\Longrightarrow \sum_{i=n}^m |g_i(x)|<\frac{\epsilon}{k}\,\,,\,\forall\,x\in X\;\;,\;\;\text{so }\ldots
